## What This Platform Does

Mirellé Inspo is a nail editorial platform that creates SEO-ranked posts on its website to help nail salons, nail techs, influencers, and nail brands get discovered online. Businesses pay to be featured in posts that rank on Google locally and nationally.

There are two types of posts on this platform:

**Type A — Client Acquisition Posts**
Posts created by Mirellé to attract paying clients. These rank on Google when salon owners, nail techs, brands, or influencers search for ways to grow their business. Each post addresses a specific pain point, presents Mirellé as the solution, and ends with a CTA to email contact@mirelleinspo.com.

**Type B — Deliverable Posts**
Posts created for paying clients once they place an order. These are the actual features, spotlights, roundups, and campaign posts that rank locally and drive end-consumers to the client's business.

