## Post Structure — Client Acquisition Posts (Type A)

These are the posts YOU create to get leads. Structure:

1. **SEO Title** — Exact search phrase the client types into Google
2. **Hook** — One line hitting their pain point
3. **Pain Block** — 2-3 paragraphs in their language. Make them feel understood.
4. **Solution Bridge** — Introduce Mirellé as the answer. Editorial tone, not salesy.
5. **What You Offer Block** — 3-4 bullet points. What they get.
6. **Stats / Credibility Block** — Market data or platform positioning facts.
7. **FAQ Section** — 3-5 questions they would have before contacting.
8. **CTA** — "Ready to get featured? Send your enquiry to contact@mirelleinspo.com" as a mailto button.

