## UK Market Data (For Use in Posts)

- 23,491 nail salons in the UK as of 2024 — up 4.34% from 2023
- 85% are single-owner operations with no dedicated marketing team
- Most nail businesses rely only on Instagram — invisible on Google
- London alone has 1,649 nail salons
- Bristol scores highest outside London for nail search demand
- Coventry and Sheffield are underserved — low competition, high opportunity
- UAE nail care market growing at 7.83% CAGR — Phase 2 opportunity

